#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.ktimetracker.appdata.xml:28 org.kde.ktimetracker.appdata.xml:37
msgid "KTimeTracker"
msgstr "KTimeTracker"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.ktimetracker.appdata.xml:29
msgid "Personal Time Tracker"
msgstr "Osebni sledilnik porabe časa"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.ktimetracker.appdata.xml:31
msgid ""
"KTimeTracker helps you track your personal time spent on various tasks and "
"projects."
msgstr ""
"KTimeTracker vam pomaga spremljati vaš osebni čas, porabljen za različne "
"naloge in projekti."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.ktimetracker.appdata.xml:32
msgid ""
"It is useful for tracking billable hours and can report the hours logged by "
"task and day."
msgstr ""
"Uporaben je za sledenje plačljivih ur in lahko poroča o prijavljenih urah po "
"dejavnostih in dnevih."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.ktimetracker.appdata.xml:33
msgid ""
"With KTimeTracker, you can organize a broken-down project as subtasks with "
"unlimited nesting. The standard keyboard and mouse shortcuts are simple and "
"make the tool really comfortable and intuitive to use."
msgstr ""
"S programom KTimeTracker lahko organizirate razčlenjen projekt kot podrejene "
"dejavnosti z neomejenim gnezdenjem. Običajne bližnjice na tipkovnici in "
"miški so preproste in omogočajo, da je orodje resnično udobno in intuitivno "
"za uporabo."
